OL,6,FA man who caused his father a fatal
OL,7,Fcardiac arrest after throwing a brick
OL,8,Fat him as he drove his van has been
OL,9,Fjailed for manslaughter.
OL,11,FThomas Dear, 20, claimed he was acting
OL,12,Fin self-defence when he threw the
OL,13,Fbrick through the vehicle's open
OL,14,Fwindow on 16 June.
OL,16,FHis father, 38-year-old Thomas Dear
OL,17,FSenior, suffered a head injury but
OL,18,Fcarried on driving following the
OL,19,Fincident on Windsor Road in Newark.
