OL,6,FA short time later he suffered a
OL,7,Fcardiac arrest at the roadside on
OL,8,FLombard Street.
OL,10,FA Home Office pathologist said the
OL,11,Fseizure was linked to the head injury.
OL,13,FDear denied murdering his father but
OL,14,Fadmitted manslaughter during an
OL,15,Fappearance at Nottingham Crown Court.
OL,17,FHe claimed he threw the brick after
OL,18,Fhis father drove at him.
