OL,3,CDad died at the wheel after son threw
OL,4,Cbrick at him
OL,6,FThe court heard the incident happened
OL,7,Fafter the pair had argued over Dear's
OL,8,Fwish to leave the traveller community.
OL,10,FCCTV showed him throwing pieces of a
OL,11,Fbroken plant pot at his father, who
OL,12,Fthen threatened his son with a garden
OL,13,Ffork.
OL,15,FDear, of no fixed address, was
OL,16,Fsentenced to three years and four
OL,17,Fmonths in a young offenders'
OL,18,Finstitution.
