OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Ruby Burrow, of
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "Whilst
OL,8,FDear may not have set out to
OL,9,Fintentionally kill his father, his
OL,10,Fdangerous and deliberate actions have
OL,11,Fresulted in the most devastating and
OL,12,Firreversible of consequences.
OL,14,F"The impact on Mr Dear's family and
OL,15,Ffriends has been simply immeasurable,
OL,16,Fhaving to endure the loss of a loved
OL,17,Fone in such sudden and traumatic
OL,18,Fcircumstances.
